
GaugeEngine.  Gauges using libgnomecanvas and XML or other based config files
defining gauge look/feel (photorealistic and scalable if possible)

Works in progress:
	Moving of interrogation profiles to external files. (complete 8/1/04)
	defining of realtime vars and derived variables outside of the code
and loaded after interrogation sequence completes.  (in design and initial 
implementation stages (8/7/04).
	Defining of all major controls outside of the sourcecode and loaded
after interrogation procedure completes.  (in design, implementation scheduled
for sept/oct 2004)  This will allow massive customization by end users...

